snippet.title: Star Gods - Steam Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Star Gods is now available on Steam! 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1179500/Star_Gods/

Check out  Phoenix Rising. They did the music for the trailer. The song is called The Edge of Nothing. https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCYdw3M-X5a5KsuIrsX3fKWA
